                    h3 Ceremony
                    p The wedding ceremony begins at 5:30 PM and  will take place outside, weather permitting.
                    p Parking is available inside the Country Club, next to the main Banquet Hall.

                .card.second
                    h3 Reception
                    p Cocktail hour will start at 6PM on the club house balcony.
                    p The reception will begin at 7 PM in the Banquet Hall.
                    p Dinner will be provided, followed by music and dancing.

